{"tid":2507841,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"辱华？中国《英雄聯盟》7位角色被改名","createTime":"2021-04-28T09:38:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T09:43:55.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d5395b14caee6060bcdebfea0f069b68b13833dd","tid":2507841,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:38:26.000Z","msg":"中國《英雄聯盟》於今（28）日更新了自家11.10版本的測試伺服器，共有7名英雄的別稱遭到更改，除了包含前些時候掀起辱華爭議的「瘟疫之源」圖奇以外，其他具有負面意義單字的角色別稱也通通在騰訊大手一揮之下消失了。<br />\n<br />\n2019年11月，中國廣電總局宣布《關於防止未成年人沉迷網路遊戲的通知》，對於玩家及遊戲內容列出了程度不等的限制性舉措。當時網易旗下的非對稱競技手遊《第五人格》便表示為了配合國家政策，將「文字上的血」及「負面意義單字」以別的名稱替代。<br />\n<br />\n如今，騰訊也針對《英雄聯盟》中國伺服器有辱華嫌疑或負面意義的英雄別稱進行改動，以下為改動的前後對比：<br />\n<br />\n艾克：時間刺客&rarr;時間奇才<br />\n<br />\n達瑞文：榮耀行刑官&rarr;榮耀刑裁官<br />\n<br />\n圖奇：瘟疫之源&rarr;瘴地怪鼠（別稱改動最大，直接換了一個名字）<br />\n<br />\n布蘭德：復仇焰魂&rarr;灼心焰魂<br />\n<br />\n卡利斯：虛空掠奪者&rarr;虛空掠食者<br />\n<br />\n雷尼克頓：荒漠屠夫&rarr;荒漠狂沙<br />\n<br />\n葛雷夫：法外狂徒&rarr;槍火狂徒<br />\n<br />\n至於改名的原因為何？目前騰訊尚未明確說明。不過中國當局近年針對影視娛樂相關產業施行了多種審核政策，也許騰訊更改英雄別稱的舉動，只是為了盡可能避免來自「黨」的麻煩。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/辱華-中國-英雄聯盟-7位角色改名-090513210.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%E8%BE%B1%E8%8F%AF-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E8%8B%B1%E9%9B%84%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F-7%E4%BD%8D%E8%A7%92%E8%89%B2%E6%94%B9%E5%90%8D-090513210.html&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0lLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=90ad8213\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/辱華-中國-英雄聯盟-7位角色改名-090513210.html</a>"},{"pid":"ebcc710113083bbcc8b2c14a44bc94642b4864d6","tid":2507841,"uid":359745,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:39:26.000Z","msg":"瘟疫之源崩口人忌崩口碗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85010f4e59152bab2d6695c3e9917f5f65b500c0","tid":2507841,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:39:53.000Z","msg":"瘟疫之源 改動最大<br />\n笑咗"},{"pid":"167d5911b245aef1e315661e626214401bb01ccf","tid":2507841,"uid":246861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:40:01.000Z","msg":"瘴地怪鼠 牛b死了"},{"pid":"b21c416af4b202a7e48695efdedaca8cdd845cf0","tid":2507841,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:40:06.000Z","msg":"稱號當名用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e11e1e5ac432a1c5013867492d028df8b6442915","tid":2507841,"uid":23749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebcc710113083bbcc8b2c14a44bc94642b4864d6","tid":2507841,"uid":359745,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:39:26.000Z","msg":"瘟疫之源崩口人忌崩口碗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:40:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"486a78e9aa60ba7b3e244721705e6d8e3e8a4749","tid":2507841,"uid":128568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:40:39.000Z","msg":"佢唔講其實唔會聯想到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3abf91b3891b286154db556ff32df73317e57b19","tid":2507841,"uid":7818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:42:05.000Z","msg":"掠食者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68500ebece47488a28853dbba68b0c08f40c5f32","tid":2507841,"uid":260271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:42:49.000Z","msg":